<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.3.2">
<l>pēymakaṭ koṅkainañ cuṇṭa piḷḷaipa ricitu veṉṟāl</l>
<l>mānila māmakaṇ mātar kēḷvaṉi vaṉeṉṟum vaṇṭuṇ</l>
<l>pūmakaṇ ṇayaka ṉeṉṟum pulaṅkeḻu kōviyar pāṭi</l>
<l>tēmalar tūvava ruvāṉ cittira kūṭattuḷ ḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When, indeed, was this the nature of a child who ate the poison</l>
<l rend="indent">of the demoness’ breast?</l>
<l>The one who appeared so the gopis, who fill the senses,</l>
<l rend="indent">scattered honeyed flowers,</l>
<l>Singing “[But] he is the beloved sweetheart to the great lady</l>
<l rend="indent">who is the great earth;</l>
<l>He is the lord to the lady of the flower where bees sip,”</l>
<l rend="indent">he is the one present in Citrakūṭam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
